    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine condition, still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently and powerfully, and the transmission shifts with absolute precision. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended, making this an ideal choice for a collector or a buyer seeking a like-new experience.",
