    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative example of automotive engineering, this vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. Every facet of this motorcar has been preserved to the highest standard, manifesting in a flawless exterior luster and a cabin that remains entirely unblemished. Meticulously maintained and subject to a rigorous multi-point inspection, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, offering the discerning driver an unparalleled experience of luxury and reliability. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection of this investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 46500.0,
