    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself how gorgeous it is!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
