    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or stone chips, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and show no signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-backed service history and a drive that is as tight and responsive as a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence that has been pampered since day one.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
